            <thetext>The inspector doesn&#39;t work properly in Inline-skeleton-based apps, since there 
the layout of the root window is only Basic (Inspector anticipating Canvas or 
similar). 

Asserts fail in inspector.components.Selector._createCatchClickLayer():

  this._root.add(this._catchClickLayer, {left: 0, top: 0, right: 0, bottom: 0});

Firebug messages:

  Assertion error! The property &#39;right&#39; is not supported by the Basic layout!: 
Called assert with &#39;false&#39;</thetext>
